OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and occasional
OL,6,Fshowers through the day, some of which
OL,7,Fcould be heavy and thundery during the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Winds are light but breezy
OL,9,Falong the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers easing during the
OL,12,Fearly evening, then clouding over from
OL,13,Fthe west with rain arriving during the
OL,14,Fevening. Feeling cool in the
OL,15,Fincreasingly breezy wind.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FCloudy and breezy, with rain
OL,18,Fclearing to the east during the
OL,19,Fmorning. Then followed by frequent
OL,20,Fheavy showers in the afternoon and
OL,21,Fwell into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
